Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:06.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was still little...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.19,0:00:15.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, riding the green bike I always used to ride, I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:22.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"How far can I go without turning back?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:28.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what exactly I was trying to do at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:36.31,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,400)}nakushita yakusoku wa hoshi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:36.31,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,400)}Send the lost promises to the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:42.69,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,400)}omoide wa tokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:42.69,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,400)}My memories won't fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:57.40,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}yotsuba no clover sagashinagara kimi no kao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:57.40,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I steal a glance at you as we look for four-leaf clovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:01:03.64,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}chirari nusumi mite wa me o sorasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:01:03.64,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But then divert my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:09.08,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}yasashii ame wa furu watashitachi no ue ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:09.08,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The gentle rain falls above our heads
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:14.62,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}surechigau hito no kazu dake dramatic ni naru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:14.62,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}as it becomes as dramatic as the number of people passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.89,0:01:20.16,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}kowareta taisetsu na mono to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.89,0:01:20.16,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder if we'll ever be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.46,0:01:26.56,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}itsuka mata aeru hi ga kurukashira
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.46,0:01:26.56,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}reunite with those precious things that were broken
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.70,0:01:31.70,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}nokoshita kizuato ga kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.70,0:01:31.70,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The scars that were left behind won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:37.41,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}sorezore no basho made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:37.41,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now we must depart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.88,0:01:41.18,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}mou ikanakucha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.88,0:01:41.18,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To our own separate ways
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:10.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A six-tatami room with no bath, ten minute walk from the college.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:14.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Built twenty-five years ago, rent 38,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.91,0:02:18.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The walls are thin and hardly soundproof.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:20.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All residents are students.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:22.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The morning sun is bright since it faces east.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:26.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I arrived in Tokyo last year after getting into an art college here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:29.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised to see the campus surrounded by fields...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:32.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By the terrible taste of my own cooking...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:36.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By the high price of the public baths...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:38.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And by the huge amount of homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.56,0:02:42.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But now it's all just a part of my everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.02,0:02:46.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:49.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, what's up, Takemoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:51.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you full right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.78,0:02:53.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got some croquettes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:54.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there some for me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:56.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:57.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Croquettes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:58.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we join?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:02.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got plenty, so everyone is welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:03.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.21,0:03:06.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any mayo, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:07.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:08.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:12.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you eat even croquettes with mayo, Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:14.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:15.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:16.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring some over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:18.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:21.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the mayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:22.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, that's a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.48,0:03:25.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So how did you come across this pile of croquettes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.40,0:03:28.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Morita-senpai told me to share them with everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:30.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:32.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:34.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't seen him in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:37.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasn't this guy been gone for like twelve days?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:39.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been fourteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:40.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost half a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:44.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I really thought he died somewhere this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:47.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, this guy's a bit too shady.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:50.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He always just suddenly disappears without saying anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:54.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And then comes back later looking all worn-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:56.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He also brings back the most random stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:58.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And every time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:01.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a mysterious roll of bills in his back pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.27,0:04:04.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And it looks like it's getting bigger every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:08.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-senpai, what does Morita-senpai do for a job exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:10.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:12.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure is mysterious, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:14.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If only it were that simple...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:16.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Quick! Let me eat those croquettes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:19.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I only have 70 yen left until my next paycheck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.99,0:04:21.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought the soy sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:25.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, those are mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:27.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said that you could take them without asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:28.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sup. You think I could get some too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:30.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Go put them back right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:30.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some Worcestershire sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:34.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is still a damn huge pile.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:35.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably around ten kilos.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:37.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think I'll get sick of eating before it's all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:40.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is from the underground complex at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:42.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he took advantage of the closing time sale too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:46.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, why croquettes of all things, Morita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:49.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why croquettes when you have all that money?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:51.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you have bought for example...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:53.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...meat, or meat, or MEAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:04:57.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be laughing at us for being so poor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:04:59.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry, Hasegawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:01.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly what he wants you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:04.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like he's looking out for us though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:07.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He did get half with curry and the other half plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:09.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's probably not looking out for us at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:13.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But why isn't he sleeping in his own room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:15.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, earlier he...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:19.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this. Share with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:23.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In return, wake me up tomorrow at nine...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:27.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mo-Morita-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:31.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me to wake him up in time for his ten o'clock lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:33.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably {\i1}that{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.69,0:05:37.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When Morita-san was a freshman, he was an hour short on attendance for a course...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:42.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and so he couldn't graduate and\Nhad to stay back for an extra year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:44.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:46.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san sure is desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:50.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't he end up repeating this year too because he overslept?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:54.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That means he'll have to attend for a\Nseventh year if he's late tomorrow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:56.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\be1\move(420,15,407,15)}Ah, I'm a seventh grader...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:57.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a huge responsibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:06:07.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\be1\move(403,15,340,15)}Seventh grader...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.01,0:05:59.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Freshman classes start early, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:03.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus Morita-senpai usually can't wake up\Neven with three alarm clocks going off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:05.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, even six wouldn't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:07.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is repeat for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.39,0:06:08.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:11.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, lend me all the alarm clocks you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:13.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:16.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, you can spend up to eight years in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.32,0:06:17.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the problem here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:22.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be definitely held accountable if he oversleeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:24.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And when that happens, who knows what he'll do to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:26.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:29.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:40.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:42.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:45.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it end up like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:10.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}We will be momentarily stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:22.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Eek! Half past nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:24.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, Morita-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:27.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up! It's half past nine already! Please wake up, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:28.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:29.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:32.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Takemoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:35.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I'm awake, let me lie down for five more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:38.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pretend to be wide awake when you're actually sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:40.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:42.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:44.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.03,0:07:46.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-senpai won't even flinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:51.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san usually doesn't wake up\Nfor 48 hours after a job, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:54.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up and go on ahead to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:56.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise you'll end up just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:08:00.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do that, my campus life will turn into the\NDark Ages before I even repeat a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.92,0:08:02.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-senpai, get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:06.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he has been roughing you up your whole first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.39,0:08:08.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks good on you, Takemoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:09.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 1,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:13.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to die! He'll kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:15.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:17.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give it all we've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:21.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,First we'll try his favorite coffee milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:21.40,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\shad0\bord0.1\be1\frz-25\fnVerdana\fscx82\c&HD0DADF&\pos(315,174)\3c&HD0DADF&}Coffee\NMilk
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:25.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It will raise his blood sugar level and stimulate brain activity!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.28,0:08:30.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take a picture of you in front of\Nthe TV as proof of all your efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.95,0:08:35.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be able to fend away at\Nleast 30% of his curse using this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:38.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All this will only amount to 30%, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:39.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:40.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep calling his name for the next fifteen minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:43.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If he still doesn't wake up after that, just go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:45.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you borrow my kicking board!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the one Morita-san gave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:49.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday, Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.93,0:08:51.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:55.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:57.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, can't you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:08:59.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a kicking board!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:03.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not thinking of paying off the 10,000 yen\Nyou borrowed last month with this, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:05.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:08.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't think I need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:10.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm off to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:11.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:13.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so mean, Mayama-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:14.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake him up! You've got fourteen minutes left!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:17.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-senpai, please wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:31.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}The train will be arriving shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:33.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H000000&}Please stand behind the yellow line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.72,0:09:35.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:52.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:54.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-senpai, wake up! Morita-senpai, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:56.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-senpai, wake up! Wake up, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:57.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wake up, Morita-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:09:58.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:10:01.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen minutes have passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:09.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't blame me if you end up repeating again, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:11.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Repeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:13.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,NO MORE REPEATING!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:17.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:26.11,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,50)\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Kanji on the forehead: {\be1\3c&H000000&}"Wind"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:26.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:29.74,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.07,0:11:10.40,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0.1\be1\fs17\pos(448,407)\c&H566769&\3c&H374F54&}Speed\NLimit on\NCampus
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:15.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.62,0:11:16.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:19.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you the sausage I didn't finish this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:20.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,NO...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.62,0:11:21.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:21.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,MORE!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:23.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,NO...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:25.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,MORE!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:36.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,NO MORE!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:42.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp3\fs40}NO MORE...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:43.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morita-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:45.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,NO MORE!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:45.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Takemoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:46.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold your horses!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:47.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,NO...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:51.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...more?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.28,0:11:53.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.78,0:11:58.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't happen to make that scooter out of our trolley, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:01.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.54,0:12:04.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, we have to carry all the busts by hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:07.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even know how heavy these things are?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,0:12:09.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're fifteen kilos a piece! Fifteen kilos!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:10.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Either fix it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:12.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or pay for the damages!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.30,0:12:14.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:15.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:16.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pretend I didn't see this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:16.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:18.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-kun did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up, Mayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:21.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:24.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, like it matters who did it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:24.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're mistaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:25.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, compensate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:26.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How cheap...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:28.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Mayama, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:30.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I tell you, I didn't do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:32.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fool us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.03,0:12:33.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else could have possibly done it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:35.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So are you going to fix it or pay for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.33,0:12:45.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:59.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the wrong classroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:05.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:07.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san's got me good this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:13.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't heard you scream like that in a while, Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:14.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.03,0:13:17.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And here I thought I'd finally have some peace of mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:20.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since his target changed to Takemoto this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:23.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So was I nothing but a sacrificial offering for the past year?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:28.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so mean, Mayama-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:30.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Mayama's been roughed up by\NMorita for a long time, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:31.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you ever tell me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:34.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way Hagu, what's a kicking board?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:32.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:54.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a scooter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:59.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, who's that little person next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:05.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she your...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:06.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:11.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to fail that bad, Mayama-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.54,0:14:13.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is my cousin's daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.71,0:14:15.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be attending this school starting this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:16.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:17.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Mayama Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.88,0:14:19.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a fourth year architecture student.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:19.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:22.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,meet... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:25.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamoto Hagumi, eighteen years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:29.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She likes to make clothing and play with clay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.52,0:14:34.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, her dad is the chief investigator of\NNagano's First Criminal Investigation Section.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:37.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's devoted his life to his daughter for eighteen years...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:42.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One false move and you'll be off to kingdom come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.70,0:14:44.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't say...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:47.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:54.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.34,0:14:57.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,like to eat these together?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:02.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I... guess you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:11.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you hungry, Hagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:18.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:21.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So Morita's got some fishy job going on, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:25.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Big-hearted as usual, aren't you Hagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.49,0:15:26.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:29.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:31.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:36.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The cherry blossoms will be blooming soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:37.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten quite warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:39.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How peaceful, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:40.96,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:44.34,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so quiet and relaxing,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:48.30,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,but at the same time a bit restless...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:49.93,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.39,0:15:52.14,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,It's spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:57.81,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Such small hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:15:59.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takemoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:11.70,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:13.66,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:22.13,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've seen the moment\Nwhen someone falls in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:23.84,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:26.34,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I embarrassed about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:34.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's spring, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:35.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:39.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:41.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:43.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.03,0:16:46.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll give you the fish cake I have left over from lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:48.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:52.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:54.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:58.12,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H32&\fs90\shad0\bord0\b1\move(832,106,5,106)\c&H505A57&}Ceramics   Workshop
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:14.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Yamada-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:17.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Such brilliant finger movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.69,0:17:21.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ceramics is all about communicating with the clay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:23.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Its voice, however, is very quiet and feeble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:30.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Only those who empty their hearts and\Nstay true to themselves can hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:30.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, did you hear about Mayama from architecture?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:31.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:33.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,At that last party Yumi was all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:35.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.41,0:17:36.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:39.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama is quite notorious you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:42.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:44.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who asked her to go out with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.01,0:17:48.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yamada-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:52.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya-Ya-Yamada-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:58.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Morita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:17:59.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Morita.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:01.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the croquettes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:05.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waking me up, Takemoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.19,0:18:06.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can finally graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:08.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:09.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.07,0:18:12.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What you did earlier was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:16.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you grow taller again, Mayama?\NAre you still in your growth period?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:18.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Get real.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:20.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, people like you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:29.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:30.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:32.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.22,0:18:36.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you running away, Morita-san?
