Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.57,0:18:50.49,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}shiketteru hibi wo hete
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:50.49,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\be1}After spending days alone, watching my biscuit go soggy
