Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.00,0:19:47.92,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}boku o niramitsukeru
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:47.92,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The headstrong shy girl gives me an angry look
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:55.51,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}okashi na koibito hachimitsu tokashiteyuku
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:55.51,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The funny lover melts honey
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:20:02.39,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}chouchou musubi o hodoku you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:20:02.39,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To undo the butterfly ties
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:45.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:51.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:02.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Korobokkur!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:05.06,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs24\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Korobokkur: {\be1\3c&H000000&}little people from Ainu legends.\N(Litterally "a person under a butterbur leaf.")
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:09.48,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}mezurashii houseki ga hiroenai nara
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:09.48,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If we can't find any rare jewels
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:03.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Koro...{\1a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&}bok...kur...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:03.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Koro...bok...{\1a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&}kur...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.94,0:20:05.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Koro...bok...kur...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:19.91,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}futari no kakera de maniawaseteshimae
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:19.91,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Allow us to get by with pieces of ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:10.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:14.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll make her cry if you don't stop, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:16.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Korobokkur, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:19.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Hagu's cute no matter what she looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:27.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:37.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was still little...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.31,0:20:47.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, riding the green bike I always used to ride, I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:53.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"How far can I go without turning back?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.63,0:21:15.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what exactly I was trying to do at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:27.81,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}akanai mabuta kosutte mieru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:27.81,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I rub my heavy eyelids to reveal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:32.94,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}pastel moyou no mirai ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:32.94,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}A future in the shape of pastels
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.32,0:21:40.11,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}chiribamerareta kigou o tadoru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.32,0:21:40.11,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I follow the scattered symbols
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:44.16,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}taguri yoseta hyoujou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:44.16,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}As my expressions were pulled in closer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.16,0:21:49.96,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}nee nandakke sagashiteita mono
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.16,0:21:49.96,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Say, what was it that we were looking for again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:53.00,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}are wa soune itsudakke
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.50,0:21:53.00,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}That's right, exactly when were those days
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.96,0:22:00.43,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}bokura ga inryoku ni sakarai nagara deatta koro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:22:00.43,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}When we used to meet, denying the attraction\Nthat was forming between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:06.35,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}sore ga waltz no you dane fushigi sa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:06.35,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}It's like a waltz, isn't it? It's quite marveling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.35,0:22:12.52,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}sasayaku youna komorebi no kousaten de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.35,0:22:12.52,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}We paint away sceneries
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.69,0:22:18.78,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}futari waltz no youni ne mawari nagara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.69,0:22:18.78,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}As we waltz and spin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.99,0:22:24.91,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}egaki dashite yuku mono
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.99,0:22:24.91,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}Where the whispering sunlight falls through the trees and meet.
